Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.44,sign_96_2_Strawberry_Custa,Food(L),0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry\NCustard\NDanish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.44,sign_96_3_Green_Tea,Drink,0000,0000,0000,,Green Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.44,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:10.65,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,we're changing seats today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.63,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll be saying goodbye \Nto my seat in a few hours, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.31,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:23.27,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on where he's seated, \Nhe can't slack off carelessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:27.25,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured changing seats would be \Na significant event for Tanaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:30.97,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,But he's calmer than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:35.63,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's cast some kind of spell on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:39.04,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So he is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:44.46,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already getting excited to see \Nwhich seat I'll get. I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:48.88,Tanaka_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope I don't get the front row center seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.19,Tanaka_Main,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.79,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, the front row is the least popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:57.90,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Is the back corner seat the \Nmost relaxing for you, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:03.08,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:08.34,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,This morning's horoscope said, "Your luck \Nwill go down if you talk during a meal,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:09.71,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,so can you be quiet, Ohta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:12.30,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.51,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just an event for him... \NHis eyes look as though he's going to war!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:21.25,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had a front row seat, \Nfrom middle school up through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:23.02,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:24.55,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:26.26,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice flag, Katou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.20,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wish misfortune on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:31.32,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems to be \Ngetting pretty complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:35.50,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,They won't stand a chance against my \Nfeelings toward this seating change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.37,sign_2366_30_Long_Homeroom,Board,0000,0000,0000,,Long Homeroom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.37,sign_2366_31_Seating_change,Board,0000,0000,0000,,Seating change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:50.72,Tanaka_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka... Don't be so openly listless \Nright after changing your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.42,Tanaka_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:57.05,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's probably drooping,\Nactually, not being listless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.18,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, this is dreadful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:02.62,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,This seat is abnormally \Nclose to the blackboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:07.39,Tanaka_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. That's not a blackboard, \Nit's Ohta's back, Miyano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:12.11,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,So does this mean I can't see \Nanything at all from this seat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:16.36,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miyano... I never thought I'd be \Nseated in front of you, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:21.46,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the way of your studies if I stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:22.62,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, we can—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.16,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Miyano-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:29.02,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,you can switch with me \Nand take the front seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.86,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:31.97,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.81,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Yes, I would \Nlike to switch with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.26,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.82,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Miyano-san, thank you for being small!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.79,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now, Ohta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.90,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not how far back the seat is that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:56.11,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,The best seat is the one right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:03:00.07,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,You provide a defensive barrier \Nand a sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.49,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I have mixed feelings about that, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:07.51,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't believe a series of coincidences
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:12.14,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,resulted in such an ideal ending, \Neven though I had all but lost hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:17.09,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a reward for my \Nconsistently good conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.10,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because of the spell you cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:27.51,Tanaka_Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun\NIs\NAlways\NListless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.52,Tanaka_Ep_Number,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.52,Tanaka_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun's Happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.85,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a few days since I was \Nseated next to Tanaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:39.24,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that our physical distance has shortened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.11,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a chance to get emotionally closer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.28,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best to talk to him more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.30,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.86,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.55,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I only said, "Ah, yeah"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.31,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,And it was to Ohta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:30.37,sign_6099_69_Mathematics_I,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Mathematics I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.50,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let this go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:25.51,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be time for the next seat change before \Nanything happens, and that'll be the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.14,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.62,sign_6483_73_Grasp_a_Teenage_,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Grasp a Teenage Boy's Heart\N10 Methods
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.62,sign_6483_74_Morning_greeting,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Morning\Ngreetings first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.90,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning greetings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:37.31,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it is the most natural \Nway to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:40.47,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So making eye contact is the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.72,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,My chance to put it into practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.93,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tanaka-kun, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.50,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:54.14,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,No good! His eyes are still closed \Nmore often than not at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.60,sign_7053_82_Get_his_attentio,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Get his attention\Nwith your femininity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.73,sign_7112_83_Brush_your_hair_,Box,0000,0000,0000,,Brush your hair back with your fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:04.36,sign_7112_83_Brush_your_hair_,Box,0000,0000,0000,,Overly long sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.40,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,The cuffs will stretch out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:18.04,sign_7112_83_Brush_your_hair_,Box,0000,0000,0000,,Sex appeal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:11.82,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Even an amateur like me knows this \Nis probably the least likely to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.36,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll give it a shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:18.04,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gosh, it's so hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.50,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.47,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most piercing \Nlook he's ever given me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:29.55,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only thing he reacted to, \Nbut it's more than I can bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.01,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to capture a teenage boy's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.52,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to capture Tanaka-kun's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:39.11,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Tanaka-kun tends to zone out a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.58,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe emphasizing my \Ndevotion would work best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.24,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,My feminine appeal is gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:51.09,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a tissue. It's the moisturizing \Nkind, so it's gentle on the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:48.95,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ta—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.16,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.75,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't take notes on the last English class...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.21,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll lend you mine so you can copy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.26,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Tana—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.42,sign_8613_104_Classical_Japane,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Classical Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:02.42,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot the handout were using in \Nclassical Japanese this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.76,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go make a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.75,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Ohta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.84,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,That was the flag for putting \Nour desks together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:20.05,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I was able \Nto talk to him more naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.33,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,before he knew who I really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.70,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back to those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.60,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but he did mention that \NI was too sparkly and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.16,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,which made me unapproachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.02,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.19,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I should go back to that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:42.15,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing everything I've \Ngained in the name of love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:47.30,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,is one way to resolve this, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:51.64,Tanaka_Italics,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but it sounds \Nvery mature for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.97,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.68,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.80,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.74,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miyano-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.88,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing big...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.07,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Just having problems getting \Nalong with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.73,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm hard to open up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.07,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.17,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,You're a wonderful person, Shiraishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.66,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Please have more faith in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.94,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! The harder you \Nwork, the luckier you'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.82,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.19,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Miyano-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.18,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. Hard work will pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.12,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miyano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:36.06,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best to make this roma—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:39.34,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,th-this friendship a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:43.83,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit! Take the \Ninitiative and get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.65,sign_11142_137_3_days_later,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,475)}3 days later
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:49.53,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shiraishi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.49,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.97,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to make you go out \Nof your way for me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:59.15,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to bother yourself with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.21,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I like being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.49,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,It backfired!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.74,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:27.22,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed that if you try hard, \Nlearn, and never give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:31.52,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,you can accomplish anything, \Nand that's what I've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:35.70,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess people's feelings \Njust don't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.83,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,How do you overcome something that \Ncan't be resolved with effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.92,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.26,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,If it can't be resolved with effort, \Nthen don't put any in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.95,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-T-Tanaka-kun, \Nyou were here all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.98,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was alone, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.33,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:09.05,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,And Ohta went home already \Nbecause his sister is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.49,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.99,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it okay to fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.91,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because even if you fail today, \Nthere's still tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.33,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,or the day after that, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.21,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It may even get resolved a year from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:35.53,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Life is long, so even if you \Ncan't do anything about it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.68,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,it will work out in the end, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.75,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't sound convincing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.69,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,That was just sort of flaky and \Nunreliable... Totally irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.69,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the type of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:59.53,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm starting to feel like things \Nwill work out. I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:05.24,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,To think I was in such a hurry to get\Ncloser to someone this laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:09.46,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know anything about Tanaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.21,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tanaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.25,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my time and stop rushing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.43,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Shimura. That's Tanaka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.90,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.71,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:52.92,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you take the first step up \Nthe stairway to adulthood before me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.30,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know what you mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.67,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd rather take the elevator \Nto adulthood if I have to go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.14,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:06.77,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... You've already \Nreached the "kissing" step?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.89,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just meant it's a pain to climb up stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:12.50,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:16.35,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! I'm gonna have to \Ngo all-out to celebrate with you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.65,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.65,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Shimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.41,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.37,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka... has a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:26.37,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.62,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.55,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,We saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:33.59,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka was walking with a quiet-looking \Ngirl with glasses and braided hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.49,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Braided? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.13,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't my girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:46.60,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so modest. If she's not \Nyour girlfriend, then who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.99,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It was Shirai—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:53.65,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can you please keep this look \Na secret from everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.48,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,A friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.22,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.97,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see you going to the trouble of making \Nfriends with someone from another class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.61,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,And a girl, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.24,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You make a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.00,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Then she was my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.50,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. If you're gonna lie, \Nat least put some effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.35,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:16.09,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,The old-model Shiraishi is suddenly \Nthe one drawing attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.02,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,And, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:22.55,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of happy they think \NI'm Tanaka-kun's girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.05,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.17,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:30.35,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on. Fess up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.01,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun needs help...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.14,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shimura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.47,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun is denying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:36.43,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe she really was just a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.48,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non. Don't worry, Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.63,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,He's only saying that to \Nhide his embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:46.44,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he keeps denying it proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:50.33,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a defiant teenager \Nwho's being contrary on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:55.08,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,You see, men don't actually mind\Nthese things as much as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.79,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, four-eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.85,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... They don't actually mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:05.03,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know how a guy's mind \Nworks, so this is very informative!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:09.01,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shiraishi-san, don't fall for it that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.93,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, I never would've \Nguessed you had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.85,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:19.86,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry. As your friend, \NI'll support you in any way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.10,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:24.11,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I would appreciate \Nit if you'd invite me along
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.76,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,when you two go out to eat something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.70,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Ohta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.27,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's a little sad to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:33.23,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be walking home alone from today on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.50,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine, Ohta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.21,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,You can carry us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.00,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if a boyfriend should be saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:45.61,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,You had a girlfriend, \Nyet you concealed it flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.62,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,You kept your cool all this time!\NYou're such a great Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.51,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Very mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.52,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.72,sign_19898_238_Rawr,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Rawr
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.72,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Here's another annoying person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.94,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't be bothered to argue anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:02.83,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you could've at least told us, your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:08.94,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about how a certain \Nperson must feel, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.92,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Master! You nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.12,sign_20474_246_Sting,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,766)}Sting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.76,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.80,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Going to see your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.71,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce us soon, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.42,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.63,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Tanaka. Say hi to your girlfriend for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.18,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.06,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.55,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes... I've never seen Tanaka look so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.24,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we went a bit \Noverboard with the teasing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:50.57,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no! Tanaka-kun had \Na fight with his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.39,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll talk to Ohta-kun and find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:56.41,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,to tell the other two it's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.11,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:08.17,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay, Shiraishi-san! \NLet's go have a drink! Some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.64,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... This version of me just \Ngot rejected! This is so confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.60,Tanaka_Main,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ohta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.18,Tanaka_Main,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual to see you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.06,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Echizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.77,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Tanaka has a girlfriend now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.86,Tanaka_Main,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,A girlfriend?! Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.45,Tanaka_Main,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:28.31,Tanaka_Main,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, he suddenly seems so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:31.43,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's a happy occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.74,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,We should be happy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.95,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Echizen, I know it's weird to ask this \Nof you out of the blue, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.29,Tanaka_Italics,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.29,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go out, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.00,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Echizen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.04,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,can I carry you under my arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.72,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel something \Nis missing right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:03.86,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of drama lately, \Nso it hasn't been this quiet in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:08.89,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well spend a quiet, \Nrelaxing day alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.38,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,If only Ohta were here at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.71,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.55,Tanaka_Main,Lady1,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:35.05,Tanaka_Main,Lady2,0000,0000,0000,,Can we have a moment of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.81,Tanaka_Main,Lady2,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to talk to you \Nabout this great product!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.52,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,If only Miyano-san were here \Nat a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:44.85,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me tell {\i1}you{\i0} about \Nhow great this guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.45,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,If only Shimura were here at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.61,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, my goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:57.98,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna exchange email addresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:58.66,Tanaka_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:03.54,sign_24446_289_Haa___,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2524,320)}Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:07.80,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,How odd... I was planning to relax alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.46,Tanaka_Italics,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't relax alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.67,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. Tanaka is all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:23.02,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,He was definitely with a girl with \Nbraided hair and glasses yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.92,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Braided hair? Glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.35,Tanaka_Italics,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Something about that bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.12,sign_25208_296_Inbox_Incoming_E,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox\NIncoming Email\NShiraishi\NIncoming Email\NShiraishi\NIncoming Email\NShiraishi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.28,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ohta-kun... Ohta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.09,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that's not his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:44.13,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,She's a friend of ours and my \Npersonal mentor, Master Macaron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.37,Tanaka_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Master Macaron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.63,Tanaka_Main,Rino,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:53.71,Tanaka_Main,Rino,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Brother? \NYou look more listless than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.16,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Rino...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.80,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I realized something today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.02,Tanaka_Main,Rino,0000,0000,0000,,Realized what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:03.43,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Ohta is absolutely essential in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.65,Tanaka_Italics,Rino,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Ohta! What have \Nyou done to my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.87,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I realized how much I appreciate everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:17.49,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that no man can live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.96,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tanaka! It was a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.68,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry! Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:34.24,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,we should've realized it was strange \Nwhen even Ohta didn't know about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:38.27,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of our apology, if there's \Nanything we can do for you, just ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.93,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I can carry you in place of Ohta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.22,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:46.35,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you guys to be your usual selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.44,Tanaka_Main,Shimura,0000,0000,0000,,You're very forgiving, \Ndespite how you look, Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.86,Tanaka_Main,Katou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved. I thought \Nyou'd never speak to us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:58.07,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Master! I'm sorry I called you a nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.78,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.24,Tanaka_Main,Miyano,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow you for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.65,Tanaka_Main,Echizen,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka! What have you done to Myaano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.42,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ohta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.12,Tanaka_Main,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry I didn't realize sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.83,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tanaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.55,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.84,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.52,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,It made me realize some important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:34.65,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's reactions when they \Nthought I had a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.99,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,If it causes that much drama, \NI'd rather not ever have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.28,Tanaka_Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.17,Tanaka_Main,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:47.02,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,I know they say "you reap what you sow," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.75,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,Not... Not ever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:55.48,Tanaka_Italics,Shiraishi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I decided not to rush things. \NI'm going to take my time.
